Summon your ugly duckling minion. Will he turn into a graceful swan? Inquiring minds want to know.<tab>After suffering countless barbs from his bullying brothers, this tiny cloudkin had enough and left its home on Neverreap to find someplace he'd be called beautiful, too.<tab>Hiss at me, he did;
fierce as goose, he was.
   - Jezul Ahuatan<tab>Miserable Company<tab>Delivers an attack with a potency of 230 to all enemies within range.
